<br />Would <em>In The Groove</em> for PS2 (alleged patent infringement, currently under litigation), <em>Tet&#1103;is: The Soviet Mind Game</em> (trademark infringement), and every other Tengen game (copyright infringement of 10NES due to unclean hands) count?

		

